                    <span>This is one of my favorites from The Rich Dad Poor Dad series. Although I find Robert's work often too generalized, he puts some broad  based tactical information in this book. I've found with all of Kiyosaki's books and tapes you have to get repeated exposure to get everything out of them. If you've already been investing and/or building a business you may find this a bit too topical but I still found it useful.
<br />
<br />Bill White
<br />Pres/CEO
<br />thebiggestdeal.com
<br />and cofounder of sleepyourwaytoriches.com</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Another Great Book by Robert</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
