                    <span>Kiyosaki is an excellent author.  For anyone in search of wealth, this is definitely the place to start.  The lessons found in the Rich Dad series are important concepts that anyone can learn from.  Apply these concepts to your own life and the possibilities are endless.  I also recommend Stop Working by Rohan Hall which guides one through building cash flow and becoming a "B" and an "I".  </span>
                  
              
